main event: A resident of El Campo, Texas observed a bright object in the sky that was traveling in a circular pattern on October 14, 1965.
interesting points: The object was described as being larger than a star,It emitted sounds for about 2-3 minutes before becoming silent,No exhaust or vapor trails were observed,The object was extremely bright and circular in shape,There have been multiple sightings reported by residents in the area.
witness description: a resident of El Campo who observed strange lights in the sky
